          </external-xref>)</cato:entity> is amended—</text>
				<paragraph id="H766DEE310F214409A544264B9908636D">
          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <text>in the matter preceding <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:i">clause (i)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking <quote>, during any period</quote>;</text>
