            <enum>(A)</enum>
            <text>by striking <quote>during which</quote> and inserting <quote>during any period during which</quote>; and</text>
					</subparagraph>
          <subparagraph id="H84B9B6FDC8784D1B90E35798B94EA657">
            <enum>(B)</enum>
            <text>in the matter following <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iii/scl:II">subclause (II)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking <quote>or</quote> after the semicolon;</text>
					</subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H437083F194AE4BBB9FA680C2A50E4F51">
          <enum>(5)</enum>
          <text>by redesignating <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iv">clause (iv)</cato:entity-ref> as <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:vi" proposed="true">clause (vi)</cato:entity-ref>;</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H3393A51280A04324A8CD92D0D014FF52">
